_sText:
Hey and thanks for checking out my first Prefab.
This is a Jail/Cell prefab for CSS, It's was designed for Hosties mod but can be used for a Jail or bunker in a map. The two Windows in the cells are breakable by the T's or CT's. Theres also a secret weapon behind the cabinets. If you dont want it there. get rid of it... Theres three versions of the Prefab. Retextures really. Dust, Metal and City. If you use this prefab, Please credit me in the authors list or in your Readme/Notes. Please dont re-upload this anywhere without my Permission. Files included in File: All the VMF's of Cells All Log files of the Cells. Screenshots included. __ Thanks Sharpblade Studios for Ideas and Help. Enjoy! - Slik.
